{"tid":1597143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我搭黨鐵感覺到大家歸位了，真的","createTime":"2019-09-26T23:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T02:40:12.000Z","uid":279068,"like":28,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b631306a6e82fc29c5e5f55630f08cbc70302689","tid":1597143,"uid":279068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T23:45:23.000Z","msg":"成日話9月少咗人，少咗文宣，呢樣唔呃得人。但尋日喺黨鐵（sorry我搭咗）收到airdrop，又提醒我要drop 下俾人，跟住喺連登又搵到好多靚文宣喎。真係靚咗又多咗嘢揀。<br />\n<br />\n回程時又drop，點知又有人回禮。今朝搭巴士drop，雖然得三四個人，但佢地係100%收文宣！<br />\n<br />\n我感覺，大家歸位了。加油呀，唔好成日話咩運動就完呀，少人呀。曱甴邊有咁易完呀。<br />\n<br />\n最後送上文宣俾大家airdrop<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JuBF24B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJuBF24B.jpg&h=f72daaad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8SeHwXW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8SeHwXW.png&h=5a6ad919&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHgR9KD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHgR9KD.jpg&h=a0df98ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u05SUbj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu05SUbj.jpg&h=3d5e26b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tpMebk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tpMebk.jpg&h=f1ca87f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18XaFRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18XaFRm.jpg&h=11dee12f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUZwqh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUZwqh2.jpg&h=892af64f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zgewqh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzgewqh3.jpg&h=8cfcc4ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bXvrYC3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbXvrYC3.jpg&h=afe112b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https: